Patch for pgAdmin 4 version 6.x.
Old notes: This product can only be installed 32-bit or 64-bit on one windows device. If pgAdmin 4 with 32-bit (64-bit) architecture is installed, try to install new version with 64-bit (32-bit) architecture, it will pop up UI requesting product un-installation. Users are encouraged to switch to a 64-bit packages from pgAdmin 4 version 4.23 because 32-bit packages will be discontinued in future releases.
